<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= subject %></title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f3f4f6;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 40px 20px;">
          <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 18px 32px; background-color: #991b1b; color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase;">
                Urgent match alert
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 32px;">
                <img src="https://jobstack.org/email-assets/logo.svg" alt="Jobstack" width="120" style="display: block; margin: 0 0 24px 0;" />
                <h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;">No matching candidates were found</h1>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">Hi <%= adminName %>,</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">
                  A job was published, but the current matching rules returned no eligible candidates. Please review the job and consider whether the filters should be widened or the profile data should be completed.
                </p>
                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; width: 150px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Job Title</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><%= jobTitle %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 700; color: #374151; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Job ID</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><%= jobId %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 700; color: #374151; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Company</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><%= companyName %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 700; color: #374151; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Location</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><%= location %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 700; color: #374151; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Candidates Considered</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><%= candidatesConsidered %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">Reason</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563;"><%= reason %></td>
                </tr>
              </table>
                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;">
                  <tr>
                    <td>
                      <a href="<%= jobUrl %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #991b1b; color: #ffffff; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px;">Open admin dashboard</a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">
                  This alert was sent automatically by JobStack.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
